  "name": "Create and Manage API Keys in JetSend",
  "body": "<p>The API KEYS tab on the Account Settings page is where you can create new and manage existing API Keys. Click your user name on the top-right corner of the application and from the drop-down menu, select Account Settings. Then, on the Account Settings page, select the API KEYS tab.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"346\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao69AEAR.png\" width=\"700\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 346px; width: 700px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao69AEAR.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao69AEAR.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao69AEAR.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao69AEAR.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao69AEAR.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao69AEAR.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao69AEAR.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3 data-id=\"creating-an-api-key\">Creating an API Key</h3>\n<p>To create an API Key, do the following:</p>\n<ol><li>\n<p>Click your user name on the top-right corner of the application and from the drop-down menu, select Account Settings.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"User-added image\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao69KEAR.png\" width=\"332\" height=\"313\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 313px; width: 332px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao69KEAR.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao69KEAR.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao69KEAR.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao69KEAR.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao69KEAR.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao69KEAR.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/2.05T5g00000Ao69KEAR.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n</li><li>\n<p>Select the API KEYS tab, and then click CREATE API KEY.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"352\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/3.05T5g00000Ao69PEAR.png\" width=\"701\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 352px; width: 701px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/3.05T5g00000Ao69PEAR.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/3.05T5g00000Ao69PEAR.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/3.05T5g00000Ao69PEAR.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/3.05T5g00000Ao69PEAR.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/3.05T5g00000Ao69PEAR.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/3.05T5g00000Ao69PEAR.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/3.05T5g00000Ao69PEAR.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n</li><li>\n<p>Enter an API key name and click CREATE.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"User-added image\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/4.05T5g00000Ao69jEAB.png\" width=\"333\" height=\"163\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 163px; width: 333px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/4.05T5g00000Ao69jEAB.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/4.05T5g00000Ao69jEAB.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/4.05T5g00000Ao69jEAB.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/4.05T5g00000Ao69jEAB.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/4.05T5g00000Ao69jEAB.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/4.05T5g00000Ao69jEAB.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/4.05T5g00000Ao69jEAB.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n</li></ol>",
